// USE OF TRY AND EXCEPT:

>>> try:
...     print(x)
... except NameError:
...     print('Variable x is not defined in Line 2002')
... except:
...     print('Something went wrong in other lines...')
... 
Variable x is not defined in Line 2002
>>> 
>>> x=2
>>> try:
...     print(x)
... except NameError:
...     print('Variable x is not defined in Line 2002')
... except:
...     print('Something went wrong in other lines...')
... 
2

